  "text": "Alshehri et al [CITATION_1] reported a 26-year-old female with a porcine mitral bioprosthesis who presented with acute pulmonary edema secondary to obstructive valve thrombosis. A favorable outcome was observed after conservative anticoagulant treatment.",
